Class GameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.boatcorp.boatgame.GameState
  • public class GameState
extends java.lang.Object
    Creates game state used for initialising, saving and loading game. This class was added in assessment 2 to fill the new requirement of a save feature - USR20.
